AMIRI Spring-Summer 2020 inspires community defined by camaraderie, romance and youthful liberation. #AMIRI
Constructed in the Emilia-Romagna region of Italy, featuring AMIRI’s signature magnetic aux jack closure, Spring-Summer 2020 introduces a new variation on the classic Amp Bag. #AMIRI

Woodstock’s Summer of Love liberation is echoed by relaxed tailoring that becomes contemporary stage outfits, where construction is modernized – slim to a kick flare ankle – and rendered in soulful pastel hues. #AMIRI
Taking cues from Beatnik to Bohemian, luxury rock n’ roll elements are brought to the fore and embed with new energy. #AMIRI
